{"tid":834670,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)星際傳奇1-3 猛火爆1-2","createTime":"2018-09-24T10:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T19:57:46.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ca113c994c1ed39fd37fb5b94e9344b30d3b40c7","tid":834670,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:39:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=KUq9LLTjIGhvWtn3ot1OSQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=1ff37d29\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=KUq9LLTjIGhvWtn3ot1OSQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=89cc30b0\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=KUq9LLTjIGhvWtn3ot1OSQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e4f72b2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/tsuyuan123/28d802aabba5d96173d30fc41cd52052.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Ftsuyuan123%2F28d802aabba5d96173d30fc41cd52052.jpg&h=6ae6b100&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c4/%E7%8C%9B%E7%81%AB%E7%88%86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc4%2F%25E7%258C%259B%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%2588%2586.jpg&h=946b05f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9e/RED_2_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9e%2FRED_2_poster.jpg&h=3c316e90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.太空船獵人號，在航行中遭隕石擊中不得不迫降在鄰近的行星上，四十名旅客中只有十二人存活，其中包括女船員卡洛琳&middot;佛雷、一名穆斯林長老，以及殺人犯里察&middot;雷迪，和押解他的警員強斯。 當他們在有三個太陽的星球上尋找水源，雷迪逃脫。眾人在搜尋時，其中一名留守乘客齊克，誤殺一名之前迫降星球時飛出船艙的倖存者，在埋葬被誤殺的倖存者時遭到不明生物虐殺。眾人本以為是雷迪下手，但最後發現在這星球地底下有一群畏懼光線，但十分凶惡的異形....<br />\n<br />\n2.電影劇情緊接上一集，殺人疑犯Riddick在事發五年之後仍未逃離那個充滿危險的星際，而且還被僱傭的賞金獵人追捕，因為他現在的項上人頭已值150萬，而出這筆賞金的卻是一個他曾經救過的人。後Riddick奪得賞金獵人們的飛船，前往首陽星查明原因。當來到首陽星時，又從一個元素使者那裡得知，原來是她預測到了馬歇爾王即將攻擊首陽星，所以才以此方式將Riddick吸引到首陽星上。可是Riddick到來還沒多久，馬歇爾王的大軍就已開到，並開始大肆攻擊首陽星，而Riddick也開始了拯救宇宙之戰....<br />\n<br />\n3.惡名昭彰的雷迪克（馮迪索飾）被同伴背叛後，獨自被放逐到銀河系上一個只有焦黑土壤的死亡星球，但很快的，前所未見的驚人變種怪物找上了他，在面臨這群比起之前所有敵人都還可怕的嗜血怪物的情況下，為了生存，他迫不得已只能選擇啟動一個裝置，而這也將引來所有為了得到重賞而一直追殺他的星際傭兵。爾後，雷迪克就開始了一場又一場的勢死之戰，與賞金獵人展開對決。<br />\n就在啟動裝置後，很快地訊號就引來了一批接著一批殘酷無情且暴力無比的傭兵殺手，不僅如此，昔日和雷迪克有著數不清舊帳的敵人也磨刀霍霍而來。就在一場將摧毀所有人的致命風暴即將來臨之前，雷迪克必須打敗所有為他人頭而來的星際傭兵們，才有生存下來的一絲希望......<br />\n<br />\n4.法蘭克莫西斯（Frank Moses；布魯斯&middot;威利飾演）是一名自CIA退休的前特工，被CIA的分類為RED，即為已退休而極度危險的（Retired, Extremely Dangerous），他感到退休生活十分無趣沒有變化，唯一的樂趣是每月撕毀養老金支票藉故與養老金管理人莎拉羅斯（Sarah Ross；瑪莉&middot;露易絲&middot;派克飾演）在電話裡的談天說地時間，且法蘭克對莎拉在心中漸生情愫；一日法蘭克家中突然闖入了數名傭兵，想要將法蘭克滅口，法蘭克憑著過去的矯健身手將傭兵團擊退後，發現攻擊的背後有著巨大的陰謀存在；因此為了保護所愛的人，法蘭克決定召集過去的老戰友們，來對抗陰謀的幕後黑手並揭發真相&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n5.出生入死、爾虞我詐的諜報世界裡，你要相信薑是老的辣！退而不休，寶刀未老的探員法蘭克（布魯斯威利 飾）憑著往昔經驗和過人能耐，將與他的昔日戰友再度出手，不但要拯救世界免於核子威脅，更要保全他們自己的老命...<br />\n<br />\n7 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=KUq9LLTjIGhvWtn3ot1OSQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=fa223025\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=KUq9LLTjIGhvWtn3ot1OSQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=4c1b4a98\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d646099eb36cbd172a91182146f13190ef613b89","tid":834670,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5316b98fb493f96f8a3a6e7330bd39a4c2f3f6","tid":834670,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2cd8b427a17f632025de056e310bf32549a6bf","tid":834670,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c861bc4cd1b9ea9fa0ee80c8eb3f237322eb18","tid":834670,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6be628477f2bc9b0b04e26ed16a686e0a11936","tid":834670,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T15:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d3e5a2ba17d4fccf4cf93255894482a2d6e68c","tid":834670,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f492852f6e42d9209ee038ab641d1dfa4fc75e3","tid":834670,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T17:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a17c64bfadcf52ba4cf461430828698e8edcde","tid":834670,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T19:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}